The use of polynomial partitioning and semialgebraic sets also suggests cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) as likely categories. The mention of an efficient randomized algorithm suggests cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as a possible category. Finally, the use of semialgebraic sets in range searching may also suggest cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a possible category.
